122
00:06:09,370 --> 00:06:10,730
What did you give him?

123
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:13,060
I don't know if you've bought one before.

124
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:14,210
Those stickers,

125
00:06:14,210 --> 00:06:14,980
the puffy ones.

126
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,220
Not the normal kinds.

127
00:06:16,410 --> 00:06:17,370
I remembered it was quite expensive.

128
00:06:17,370 --> 00:06:18,410
Five yuan for one sticker sheet.

129
00:06:19,890 --> 00:06:20,570
Did you buy one before?

130
00:06:20,570 --> 00:06:21,700
I did.

131
00:06:22,980 --> 00:06:25,010
How old were you?

132
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,380
Seven or eight.

133
00:06:27,410 --> 00:06:29,170
I can't really remember.
It happened when I was in Grade 3.

134
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,690
That can't be counted as a relationship.

135
00:06:33,130 --> 00:06:34,170
It doesn't count?

136
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:39,050
What is love then?

137
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:41,220
Love is when I...

138
00:06:42,130 --> 00:06:43,409
He...

139
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:12,610
You're back.

140
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:15,300
I'm cooking.

141
00:07:23,570 --> 00:07:27,490
♫ Even the pedestrians look like him ♫

142
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:35,490
♫ Even the sky won't stop crying ♫

143
