150
00:07:47,650 --> 00:07:48,570
You are cooking.

151
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:50,810
I bought some vegetables

152
00:07:51,050 --> 00:07:52,260
on my way back.

153
00:07:53,530 --> 00:07:55,010
How's your day today?

154
00:07:55,010 --> 00:07:55,850
How was work?

155
00:07:56,970 --> 00:07:57,730
Pretty good.

156
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:00,370
We exchanged many new technologies

157
00:08:00,490 --> 00:08:02,170
with specialists in pancreatic diseases.

158
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:03,340
I heard that in Germany,

159
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:04,930
they have new adjuvant therapies

160
00:08:04,930 --> 00:08:06,450
and there have been successful cases.

161
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:07,290
I'm so glad.

162
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:10,970
Will you feel bored

163
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,130
