164
00:08:12,130 --> 00:08:13,290
No, I won't.

165
00:08:13,290 --> 00:08:14,210
I like it.

166
00:08:14,210 --> 00:08:15,290
What else did you do?

167
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:17,610
I had lunch with my colleagues.

168
00:08:18,570 --> 00:08:19,170
In the afternoon,

169
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:20,820
we had a brief exchange.

170
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:21,530
Nothing else.

171
00:08:21,690 --> 00:08:22,130
How about you?

172
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:24,330
I...

173
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:26,260
I was busy making money.

174
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:27,340
Nothing much.

175
00:08:29,770 --> 00:08:30,530
You must be tired

176
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:32,610
after having a long day.

177
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:34,169
You don't have to cook.

178
00:08:34,289 --> 00:08:35,169
Let's dine out.

179
00:08:35,409 --> 00:08:35,940
It will be my treat.

180
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:37,580
Do you want Japanese or French cuisine?

181
00:08:41,850 --> 00:08:42,490
Well...

182
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:44,140
If you don't like it,

183
00:08:44,650 --> 00:08:45,820
