189
00:08:55,770 --> 00:08:56,810
Well then, I like it too.

190
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:16,860
What's the matter with you today?

191
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:19,530
Why do you keep looking at me?

192
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:24,060
You cried?

193
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:28,530
No.

194
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:30,170
Probably because that

195
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:32,970
I haven't rested well these two days.

196
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:34,980
I suppose so.

197
00:09:35,690 --> 00:09:36,860
No one would dare to bully you.

198
00:09:38,370 --> 00:09:39,850
Except for you.

199
00:09:42,890 --> 00:09:43,490
Nothing.

200
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:53,970
Ling Rui.

201
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:55,450
Today,

202
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,820
I really, really

203
00:09:57,820 --> 00:09:59,140
want to hug you today.

204
00:10:00,490 --> 00:10:01,660
Can I hug you?

205
00:10:04,450 --> 00:10:04,780
Sure.

206
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,820
I have to get some ingredients.

207
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:27,170
Okay.

208
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:39,460
Fangning,

209
00:10:41,690 --> 00:10:42,650
why are you acting

210
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:43,490
