213
00:10:46,930 --> 00:10:47,770
It's fine.

214
00:10:47,770 --> 00:10:48,410
Go on.

215
00:10:54,730 --> 00:10:55,690
Fangning, come on.

216
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:56,660
Come.

217
00:11:00,570 --> 00:11:00,970
Here.

218
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:03,090
Stand still.

219
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:04,420
Stand against the wall.

220
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:05,850
Don't move.

221
00:11:06,210 --> 00:11:06,650
What's wrong?

222
00:11:10,370 --> 00:11:11,010
What are you doing?

223
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:14,980
What's wrong?

224
00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:17,090
Put your back against it.

225
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,010
Don't let it fall off.

226
00:11:22,330 --> 00:11:22,900
Hold these.

227
00:11:24,490 --> 00:11:25,170
Grab tight.

228
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:29,490
Don't move.

229
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:30,850
Dinner will be ready soon.

230
00:11:31,450 --> 00:11:32,330
Just wait a bit more.

231
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:33,730
Be good.

232
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:36,450
If... If you do this,

233
00:11:36,930 --> 00:11:38,260
I can't move.

234
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:39,970
That's the point.

235
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:41,450
Or there's no way I can cook.

236
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:56,980
Well then...

237
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,970
What can be called as

238
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:00,410
love?

239
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:18,050
Love is when you care

240
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:21,100
if the person is happy or not.

241
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:23,570
All your emotions

242
00:12:23,770 --> 00:12:24,810
are influenced by him.

243
00:12:27,770 --> 00:12:29,570
