244
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,090
I don't want to force him

245
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:34,050
to do what he doesn't want to.

246
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:37,300
You want to help him realize all his wishes.

247
00:12:38,450 --> 00:12:40,370
You want to give him your most important things.

248
00:12:41,130 --> 00:12:42,050
All of it.

249
00:12:43,410 --> 00:12:44,250
Ling Rui,

250
00:12:46,450 --> 00:12:48,250
I would like to officially inform you that

251
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:51,380
I want us

252
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,530
to start...

253
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:57,900
I'll open the door.

254
00:12:58,330 --> 00:12:59,050
That's fine.

255
00:12:59,250 --> 00:12:59,980
I'll go.

256
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:06,170
Who's that?

257
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:08,290
Who?

258
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:12,730
Lu Fangning,

259
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:14,530
you are just forcing him!

260
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:15,740
Tang Pingping,

261
00:13:15,770 --> 00:13:17,380
why are you making a scene here at my house?

262
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,340
I didn't expect that

263
00:13:20,650 --> 00:13:21,690
you would use their family debt

264
00:13:21,690 --> 00:13:22,970
to force him to marry you.

265
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,580
