276
00:13:47,090 --> 00:13:47,930
Who gives you the right

277
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:48,850
to speculate

278
00:13:48,850 --> 00:13:49,850
my feelings?

279
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:51,620
Tang Pingping,

280
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:54,140
listen carefully.

281
00:13:54,450 --> 00:13:55,770
How did Ling Rui and I meet

282
00:13:55,770 --> 00:13:56,970
is none of your business.

283
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:58,340
Besides, I'm telling you.

284
00:13:58,780 --> 00:13:59,930
My feelings for him are real.

285
00:14:00,770 --> 00:14:01,810
As long as he's happy,

286
00:14:01,810 --> 00:14:03,020
I'll be happy.

287
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,020
If he is not,

288
00:14:04,170 --> 00:14:05,650
I'll try my best to make him happy.

289
00:14:05,940 --> 00:14:06,810
I won't let him do anything

290
00:14:06,810 --> 00:14:07,890
that he doesn't like.

291
00:14:07,890 --> 00:14:08,610
On the contrary,

292
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:09,940
I will give him

293
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,050
my most precious things.

294
00:14:11,330 --> 00:14:12,660
For the first time since I was a child,

295
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:13,770
I now understand

296
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:15,820
